11 December 2008The Minister in The Presidency, Dr Manto Tshabalala-Msimang, will in conjunction with government, business and the youth sector, host a Ministerial Imbizo and a National Youth Indaba in the North West Province between 17 and 19 December.The indaba seeks to promote social dialogue between the youth, government, business and youth development agencies.Media programme: Enquiries Charity Bhengu Cell: 083 679 7424Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)